<section class="policies">
  <h2>Store Policies</h2>

  <div class="policy-card">
    <h3>Cancelled Scheduled Requests</h3>
    <p>
      Customers are eligible to cancel requests for printing services within
      <strong>24 hours</strong> after placing their order, provided production
      has not yet begun.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="policy-card">
    <h3>Payments & Refunds</h3>
    <p>
      Customers may request to cancel payments within
      <strong>24 hours</strong> of placing an order. Refund processing times
      may vary depending on your bank and the day the request is made.
      A confirmation email will be sent once the refund has been processed.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="policy-card">
    <h3>Receipts & Confirmations</h3>
    <p>
      Confirmation receipts can also be provided through
      <strong>WhatsApp</strong> upon customer request.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="policy-card">
    <h3>Product Completion Policy</h3>
    <p>
      If a customer's order is not completed by the promised completion date
      and is delayed by more than <strong>3 additional days</strong>, the
      customer will be eligible for a refund.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="policy-card">
    <h3>Delivery Policy</h3>
    <p>
      Once an order has been completed, delivery is expected within
      <strong>24–48 hours</strong>, depending on the shipping carrier.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
